#!/bin/perl -w
#************************************************************************
#   $Version:$
#   Package	: xmt_xtest
#   Synopsis	: xtest [options] 
#   Purpose	: white box test harness: spawns IUTs under control of debuggers,
#	then uses Expect to manipulate/test IUT execution via debugger cmds.
